tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Protocol_Results (
    result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    protocol_id UUID REFERENCES Quantum_Protocols(protocol_id),
    user_id UUID REFERENCES Protocol_Users(user_id),
    completion_status VARCHAR(50),
    result_data JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE key_distribution (
  key_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  protocol_id INT,
  key_type VARCHAR,
  key_length INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (protocol_id) REFERENCES quantum_protocols(protocol_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_measurements (
  measurement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  operator_id INT,
  measurement_type VARCHAR,
  measurement_result VARCHAR,
  FOREIGN KEY (operator_id) REFERENCES quantum_operators(operator_id)
);

CREATE TABLE protocol_1 (
  protocol_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  protocol_name STRING,
  description STRING,
  security_level INTEGER
)
